    "description": "Are you a skilled Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Netsol Technologies Digital Technologies in Ghaziabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Netsol Technologies Digital Technologies:\nNetsol Technologies Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Netsol Technologies Digital Technologies!",
